<div xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml">
<div class="paragraph">
<p>This trigger event is used when person/patient allergy information has changed. It is used in conjunction with a new allergy segment, the <em>IAM - Patient Allergy Information Segment-Unique Identifier</em>, which supports Action code/unique identifier mode update for repeating segments as defined in <em>2.10.4</em>, "<em>Protocol for interpreting repeating segments or segment groups in an update Message</em>."</p>
</div>
